---- MODULE MCDieHarder ----
Here is the complete module in TLA+ with your additional configuration. This will allow you to define a function `MCMove` that moves jug from one end of Jug until it reaches its goal or exceeds capacity, and then returns whether there's any solution left (i.,e not exceeding Capacity).
